Notes: Lady Blues No. 1 in WBCA/USA Today Coaches Poll. Washburn wins 33rd straight
game tying ESU's MIAA record set in 1997-98 season. Jennifer Harris' 39 points
sets a new school record breaking Laura Mueller's 38 vs UMSL in 1991. Twenty-
two of Harris' 39 points came in second half.
Game.Officials: Phil Griffin,  Rhonda Grayson,  Tony Bickford
